com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.text.dialog

Class QueryGroupModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.text.dialog.QueryGroupModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryModel

    public class QueryGroupModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements QueryModel
    The QueryModel implementation for a Query Group. A query group comprises a logic operator, and a mixture of Query Fields (represented by QueryFieldModels) and sub-groups (represented by QueryGroupModels)
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
